description:
When God calls His people out of Babylon (Revelation 18:4), what does He call them into? Does God have a church on earth in the last days? Is there a church that fits the description of Gods remnant in the Bible? What are the characteristics of Gods church?

In this, the final episode of the series, Walter Veith looks at the Biblical characteristics of Gods church as given in Revelation 14:12. Which church is the true church according to the Bible? Find out in this episode.
